  dialogueText:
  - 
  - Captain, the ship is ready to launch. Direct trip programmed to Planet Zorbob
    for your meeting with President Blorika.
  - Copy that Commander, hopefully she's in a better mood then she was at our last
    meeting
  - Unlikely sir, the high temperature readings suggest an excessive amount of slime
    secretion for the Zorbobians
  - "*sigh* lets get this over with. Commander, what's the president's file say,
    if she\u2019s gonna be pissy might as well woo her with something, lighten the
    mood, ya know?"
  - The president's Spacebook profile suggests she enjoys long walks on the beach,
    and the sound of people chewing with their mouths open.
  - "I guess I'll have to take what I can get\u2026"
  - 'As you dock at the Space Station orbiting Blorfengarl, the ship opens up to
    a large docking bay. To greet you is a grumpy wad of goo, a spiffy looking tie
    around his neck. '
  - "Ah! Captain... You look so\u2026 intelligent. It\u2019s a pleasure to finally
    be meeting you!"
  - "Pleasure\u2019s all mine General!"
  - Your trip here was alright?
  - Good to hear!
  - HA! Apologies Captain, we meant no harm! We're due on a new Fnozzle for the artificial
    gravity core!
  - "It\u2019s no trouble, just make sure it\u2019s better for next time HAHA!!"
  - Hmm, well we have some Bleeding Grapes back at the Space Station you can have
    some of those.
  - The general turns away, a wet slurping sounds as he moves.
  - Walk with me Captain. The president is waiting in her office.
  - "By the time you make it to the President's Office, you\u2019re tugging at your
    collar, the heat making your shirt stick to your skin. When you open the door
    to the president's office, she is far from what you expected."
  - "She\u2019s a tall green skinned woman with big bug eyes, and dressed much too
    scandalously for a politician."
  - Oh wow! You're earlier than I was anticipating! You must be the captain!
  - She holds out her hand for you to shake.
  - "It\u2019s a pleasure to officially meet you Miss President."
  - "Oh please, I get enough formality from my glorbs\_ everyday, Politicia is fine."
  - Well it's a pleasure to meet you Politicia!
  - Likewise captain!
  - Politicia's outstretched hand freezes before it returns to her side.
  - "Sorry! You\u2019re just\u2026 uh\u2026 very tall."
  - I get that a lot.
  - "Well it\u2019s a pleasure to officially meet you Miss President"
  - Just Politicia is fine.
  - "Politicia's outstretched hand freezes before it returns to her side. Her lips
    purse together as if she\u2019s not sure what to say."
  - "uhh, yea\u2026 I won the election 3 terms in a row"
  - "oh! No that\u2019s not what I meant! You're just like\u2026"
  - like what? (lowkey annoyed)
  - You're not gooey!
  - What does that have to do with anything?! I thought you people were more open-minded
    then that!
  - Politicia is almost fuming. You tug at your collar uncomfortably before taking
    a deep breath.
  - "Clearly we\u2019ve gotten off on the wrong foot haha! All I meant if you look
    different then the rest of your people."
  - "Clearly we have\u2026"
  - Politicia huffs and crosses her arms, obviously offended.
  - uhh, sorry, didn't mean it that way (sweats)
  - I suppose I can ignore this, considering you bring me an offering next time we
    have a meeting.
  - "An uncomfortable silence falls over the two of you. Of course the first time
    you reach out to a new System and you've insulted their President within the
    first minute\u2026"
  - "So uhh\u2026"
  - "Anyways, now that you're here I\u2019d like to discuss the implications of the
    alliance proposal you sent over?"
  - 'Absolutely. The Human Federation have been growing and expanding and as the
    leader of the Raven Galaxy Exploratory Mission, I am looking to make some new
    allies! '
  - "Well, we are looking for some new strong allies, I\u2019m just not quite sure
    we can trust the humans quite yet, no offense!"
  - None taken!
  - "Considering you\u2019ve only established yourselves as a galactic empire fairly
    recently\u2026 I just am unsure of your human history."
  - "That\u2019s a fair concern, but just as a completely unbiased opinion, this
    Human is 100% trustworthy!"
  - You and Politicia take some time going over the alliance proposal, discussing
    details and other political mumbo jumbo, the usual kinds of conversations a politician
    would have.
  - Well, I have a lot to consider for our next meeting!
  - You take her hand, flash a cunning smirk before kissing her spikey knuckles like
    a proper gentlecaptain.
  - I look forward to our next meeting Politicia
  - "Oh my! Don\u2019t be a stranger, Captain!"
  - "I agree, there\u2019s nothing wrong with wanting more allies."
  - Until next time Politicia.
  - Of course, safe travels.
  - The End
